  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virgin is lonely. He's looking for a girlfriend. Maybe one day he will find love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The genre of the game is a walking simulator with third-person or first-person view (use mouse wheel). There is a lot of humor and interesting cutscenes in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game controls: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WASD </strong>- move </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Space bar</strong>- jump </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>C </strong>- crouch  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Left Shift</strong> - walk/run </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mouse wheel</strong> - zoom</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >P.S. The game is based on real-life experiences</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virgin is lonely. He's looking for a girlfriend. Maybe one day he will find love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The genre of the game is a walking simulator with third-person or first-person view (use mouse wheel). There is a lot of humor and interesting cutscenes in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game controls: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WASD </strong>- move </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Space bar</strong>- jump </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>C </strong>- crouch  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Left Shift</strong> - walk/run </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mouse wheel</strong> - zoom</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >P.S. The game is based on real-life experiences</p>",
